1. *Drugo* od svega, moramo da se dogovorimo oko datuma. (Secondly, we need to agree on the date.)
2. Prvo ćemo da popravimo ogradu, a *drugo* da uredimo dvorište. (First we will fix the fence, and secondly we will arrange the yard.)
3. Bio je *drugo* dete u porodici. (He was the second child in the family.)
4. *Drugo* mesto je osvojio učesnik iz Nemačke. (The participant from Germany won the second place.)
5. *Drugo* je trajalo 15 minuta. (The second one lasted 15 minutes.)